    "Generally and roughly speaking, there are various ways of producing transcriptions.",
    "Two frequently used approaches are diplomatic and semi-diplomatic transcriptions.",
    "The former transcribes as much as possible as is, taking a large character set into consideration; the latter allows for adaptations to improve readability, e.g.",
    "writing out abbreviations and simplifying some characters.",
